sbol:ComponentDefinition.addgene:aPortionOfThisPlasmidWasDerivedF: Soluble human PACE/furin ORF was obtained by PCR using plasmid SC118550 (Origene, USA) as a template, the ORF was brought in line with the reference sequence NM_002569 by adding six missing nucleotides (coding VQ).
